23:["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-white pt-16 pb-24","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container-x grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_260px]","children":[["$","article",null,{"data-progress-target":true,"className":"max-w-3xl prose-base","children":[[["$","p","0",{"className":"text-ink-200 text-lg leading-relaxed mt-6","children":"If you run a service business with more than three UK locations, the bar for local search moved twice in the last twelve months. Google's March 2026 spam update and the December 2025 Helpful Content refinement both punished thin, duplicated location pages — the exact pattern most British multi-location brands rely on. This is the playbook we're using for clients from Bristol to Aberdeen."}],["$","h2","1",{"id":"the-stack","className":"font-display font-semibold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-ink-50 mt-14 scroll-mt-24 group","children":["$","a",null,{"href":"#the-stack","className":"no-underline","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":"The local stack that actually ranks in 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"aria-hidden":true,"className":"ml-2 text-ember-500/0 group-hover:text-ember-500/80 transition-colors text-base","children":"#"}]]}]}],["$","p","2",{"className":"text-ink-200 text-lg leading-relaxed mt-6","children":"We treat UK local SEO as four interlocking layers: a clean Google Business Profile, location pages with genuine on-the-ground evidence, structured data the SERP can actually parse, and a citation profile that resolves to one canonical NAP. Get one wrong and the others underperform."}],["$","ol","3",{"className":"mt-6 space-y-3 list-none","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"flex items-start gap-3 text-ink-200 text-lg leading-relaxed","children":[["$","span",null,{"aria-hidden":true,"className":"mt-1 grid h-6 w-6 place-items-center rounded-full bg-ember-500/15 text-ember-600 text-xs font-bold shrink-0","children":1}],["$","span",null,{"children":"One Google Business Profile per physical location with manager-level access centralised at HQ."}]]}],["$","li","1",{"className":"flex items-start gap-3 text-ink-200 text-lg leading-relaxed","children":[["$","span",null,{"aria-hidden":true,"className":"mt-1 grid h-6 w-6 place-items-center rounded-full bg-ember-500/15 text-ember-600 text-xs font-bold shrink-0","children":2}],["$","span",null,{"children":"Per-location landing pages that include unique photography, named staff, and at least two embedded local reviews."}]]}],["$","li","2",{"className":"flex items-start gap-3 text-ink-200 text-lg leading-relaxed","children":[["$","span",null,{"aria-hidden":true,"className":"mt-1 grid h-6 w-6 place-items-center rounded-full bg-ember-500/15 text-ember-600 text-xs font-bold shrink-0","children":3}],["$","span",null,{"children":"LocalBusiness + Service + FAQPage schema on each location page, with sameAs pointing at the GBP listing."}]]}],["$","li","3",{"className":"flex items-start gap-3 text-ink-200 text-lg leading-relaxed","children":[["$","span",null,{"aria-hidden":true,"className":"mt-1 grid h-6 w-6 place-items-center rounded-full bg-ember-500/15 text-ember-600 text-xs font-bold shrink-0","children":4}],["$","span",null,{"children":"A single canonical NAP (Name, Address, Phone) syndicated through Yell, Thomson Local, Bing Places, and Apple Business Connect."}]]}]]}],["$","h2","4",{"id":"gbp-2026","className":"font-display font-semibold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-ink-50 mt-14 scroll-mt-24 group","children":["$","a",null,{"href":"#gbp-2026","className":"no-underline","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":"What changed with Google Business Profile in 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"aria-hidden":true,"className":"ml-2 text-ember-500/0 group-hover:text-ember-500/80 transition-colors text-base","children":"#"}]]}]}],["$","p","5",{"className":"text-ink-200 text-lg leading-relaxed mt-6","children":"Two shifts matter. First, the Q1 2026 rollout of AI-generated Place summaries means Google now writes a paragraph about your location in the local pack — pulled from reviews, your description, and Q&A. Brands with thin descriptions get bland summaries. Second, service area businesses (SABs) without a verifiable address are dropping in the 3-pack across Greater London and Manchester. If you're a SAB, get a verified address even if you don't take walk-ins."}],"$L26","$L27","$L28","$L29","$L2a","$L2b","$L2c","$L2d","$L2e","$L2f","$L30","$L31","$L32"],"$L33","$L34","$L35","$L36"]}],"$L37"]}]}]
